Company Overview of Banco BTG Pactual S.A.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Banco BTG Pactual S.A., together with its subsidiaries, provides financial products and services in Brazil and internationally. The company’s investment banking services include underwriting of public and private debt and equity products; advisory services relating to mergers and acquisitions, divestitures, restructurings, spin-offs, reorganizations, and other corporate transactions; placement and advisory services in public and private offers of equity and debt bonds; credit products and instruments, including export credit lines, collateralized loans, repos, bridge loans, securitization, guarantees, and others, as well as alternative fixed income investments; financial products and service...
Banco BTG Pactual S.A., together with its subsidiaries, provides financial products and services in Brazil and internationally. The company’s investment banking services include underwriting of public and private debt and equity products; advisory services relating to mergers and acquisitions, divestitures, restructurings, spin-offs, reorganizations, and other corporate transactions; placement and advisory services in public and private offers of equity and debt bonds; credit products and instruments, including export credit lines, collateralized loans, repos, bridge loans, securitization, guarantees, and others, as well as alternative fixed income investments; financial products and services in stocks, fixed income and equities, interest rates, and foreign exchange and commodities; and market making, brokerage, and research services. Its asset management products and services comprise equity, hedge, and fixed income investment funds; management of investment funds, private equity, infrastructure, real estate, and natural resource investment funds; and administration of investment funds. The company’s wealth management services include banking and transaction products, such as credit lines, bank guarantees, government bonds, bank deposit certificates, corporate bonds, real estate credit bills and notes, agricultural credit bills, and stocks and stock loans, as well as exchange traded and over-the-counter derivatives, structured notes, and foreign exchange spot and futures market services; portfolio investment solutions; and wealth and estate planning and retirement services, as well as advisory services for tax efficiency, succession planning, offshore investment solutions, and philanthropic projects. It also offers corporate advisory services in the areas of funding and strategic consulting. The company was founded in 1983 and is based in Sao Paulo, Brazil. Banco BTG Pactual S.A. is a subsidiary of BTG Pactual Holding S.A.
Detailed Description


