Banco BTG Pactual S.A. Key Developments

BTG Pactual Presents at Investing in LatAm Mining Cumbre, Jul-11-2017 05:00 PM
Jun 21 17
BTG Pactual Presents at Investing in LatAm Mining Cumbre, Jul-11-2017 05:00 PM. Venue: Santiago, Chile. Speakers: Nicolas de Camino, Director ­ Asset Management.


Banco BTG Pactual S.A. Announces Unaudited Earnings Results for the First Quarter of 2017
May 9 17
Banco BTG Pactual S.A. announced unaudited earnings results for the first quarter of 2017. Total Revenue was BRL 1,661 million against BRL 3,545 million a quarter ago. Adjusted net income was BRL 720 million against BRL 1,009 million a quarter ago. Adjusted income before taxes was BRL 959 million against BRL 1,736 million a quarter ago. Annualized ROAE was 18.7% against 20.1% a quarter ago. Adjusted net income per unit was BRL 0.92 against BRL 0.91 a quarter ago.  Book Value per unit was BRL 20.1 against BRL 18.4 a quarter ago. Operating income was BRL 1,211 million.


Banco BTG Pactual S.A. to Report Q1, 2017 Results on May 09, 2017
May 4 17
Banco BTG Pactual S.A. announced that they will report Q1, 2017 results After-Market on May 09, 2017


