Zitelmann, José 

 José Zitelmann  is a Managing Partner and Head of Latam Asset Management at BTG Pactual.  He was previously Head of LatAm Equity Proprietary Trading at both Banco Pactual and UBS Pactual, and was also a part of the UBS Pactual Executive Committee.  José joined Pactual in 1998, where he started working in Corporate  Finance.  A year later he switched to the Asset Management division, and  subsequently took over as Head of Equities Proprietary Trading in 2003 before becoming a Partner of Pactual in 2004. 
 José holds a BA in Business Management from Fundação Getulio Vargas (FGV-SP), São Paulo Business School. 



